<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/256518-very-good-story-except-did-communists">Very good story except....did Communists really talk like that? Every word out of a Communist&#39;s mouth in this story was completely ridiculous. If people back then actually believed that drivel, then I have even less respect for communists than I did before.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_256518'><a id="like_count_community_question_256518" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/256518?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">4 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F19494.The_Spy_Who_Came_In_from_the_Cold">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/256518-very-good-story-except-did-communists">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/256518-very-good-story-except-did-communists">See all 5 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
